   average ratio of measured:calculated) yields predicted oscillator
   strengths for transitions to upsilon = 5 and upsilon = 6 of 2.9 x
   10(-10) and 4.0 x 10(-11), respectively, corresponding to integrated
   absorption cross sections of 2.6 x 10(-22) and 3.5 x 10(-23) cm(2)
